type="local"
href="jonmsterling.xml"
addr="jonmsterling"
title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>A set <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00MH.xml"
addr="jms-00MH"
title="Countable set">countable</fr:link> if and only if the disjoint union <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A+{\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
